data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Have the charm of a Craftsman with modern conveniences! Renovated bungalow with efficiency apartment in the back. Walking distance to Florida Hospital South campus and minutes from Lake Ivanhoe and the downtown business district, this home sits on a quiet dead-end, brick street. The kitchen and all bathrooms have new solid wood cabinets, quartz and marble countertops, and marble bath tile. New stainless appliances. The main house has three bedrooms (2 master bedrooms), one unconventional bedroom or sitting room connected to the downstairs "master" bedroom, three full baths (2 ensuite), open kitchen/living/dining rooms with fireplace and an enclosed front porch for added living space.  Hardwood floors, plantation shutters, and lots of storage space. Upstairs has a second master and family room with a wet bar. Separate apartment in the back is also newly renovated with a full kitchen and bath. Perfect for an office, in-laws, or rental income. Luxury roof installed in 2016: new wiring, plumbing, and tankless hot water.
